Hi, this is Zee. Your On-Hand available expert who has expertise in website design (Wix, WordPress, Shopify, etc) and graphic Design (Photoshop & Illustrator).

let's revamp your business with my expertise and your involvement!

description.content:
Are you looking for a professional developer? Who can do WordPress website design and development for your business?


I can build, design website, redesign, clone, wordpress website development


If you already have a website for your business that looks old and outdated, you are at the right place. This is a place for all kinds of Web development services.

 

SERVICES I AM OFFERING ON THIS GIG:

  • Create, Edit, Revamp, WordPress Web
  • Fix WordPress issues
  • Business Web Design/Development
  • Mobile Friendly
  • Responsive Web
  • Social Media Integration
  • Contact Form
  • Google Maps
  • Responsive Web.
  • Fixing bug
  • Payment Integration
  • High Professional site
  • Landing pages with Elementor Pro

 

Why you choose me:

  • 24/7 Customer Support
  • Best User Experience on site
  • Responsive website
  • Experienced Developer.
  • Neat And Clean Work
  • On-time Delivery

 

If you're interested, please inbox me before placing your order.


Thanks

ZEE

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Wordpress or hosting Access.
Logo - Content - Typography - Color Scheme - Website sample you like - Any images/videos (Not necessary) If you don't have anything, don't worry, just contact me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer any support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I offer free support after order completion for 31 days

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit myself after delivery ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes of course. You will be able to edit yourself. In that case, if you face any issues, i am here to help you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I be sure that your delivery will make me satisfy?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: As I mentioned I give you unlimited revisions until you are completely happy with your final website. You will receive 100% up to your expectations.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you also do Logo design ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, you need to purchase gig extra for logo.
We will provide you multiple concepts for logo and will send all source files of your selected logo.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you able to provide Web hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, with an extra cost of $70 USD per year for the web hosting.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you able to create exact same design of link provided?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can do exact clone of your provide design,

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you help me with website Content like (images)?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we will provide you paid stock images for your website in high quality.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you guide or discuss on  zoom?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can guide about everything on Zoom meeting

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you make wordpress websites with woocommerce ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can make WordPress website using woocommerce.
